item_name: 4head Effective Headache Relief Stick (Pack of 1) FJ
item_description:
Fast, effective headache relief without pills. Applied directly to the forehead, this stick contains levomenthol (90% w/w) which creates a cooling and tingling sensation, helping to dilate blood vessels and block pain signals. Non-greasy, colourless formula suitable for on-the-go use. Can be applied as needed without waiting 4 hours between applications.

Age Restrictions: Suitable for adults and children over 12 years.

Always read the Patient Information Leaflet before use.
